阿黛尔因病暂停拉斯维加斯居住https://www.nme.com/news/music/adele-pauses-las-vegas-residence-due-to-illness-3593857?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=adele-pauses-las-vegas-residence-due-疾病Surej SinghWed, 28 Feb 2024 01:57:53 +0000 Music NewsNewsLive Music NewsPophttps://www.nme.com/?p=3593857 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/adele@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/adele@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/adele@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/adele@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/adele@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/adele@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/adele@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “遵医嘱，我别无选择，只能好好休息”</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/adele-pauses-las-vegas-residence-due-to-illness-3593857">阿黛尔因病暂停拉斯维加斯居住的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/adele@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/adele@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/adele@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/adele@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/adele@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/adele@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/adele@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/adele">阿黛尔</a>因病推迟了五周的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/adele-extends-las-vegas-residency-with-32-more-shows-3518855">拉斯维加斯驻场演出</a>。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/adele-30-album-review-dependable-pop-titan-finally-mixes-things-up-3096613">阿黛尔 – “30”专辑评论：可靠的流行巨星混合了一切</a></strong></li></ul><p>今天（2月28日），这位受人尊敬的创作型歌手在社交媒体上宣布，她必须“暂停”她长期驻场演出的五个周末的约会，并透露她在“最后一站比赛结束时”生病了。并一直贯穿我的休息时间。”</p><p>她接着解释说，她在生病期间继续参加了几场演出，但此后承受了后果：“在演出恢复之前，我还没有完全恢复健康，现在我又病了，不幸的是这对我的声音造成了影响。”</p><p> “所以，按照医生的嘱咐，我别无选择，只能好好休息。此赛段的剩余五个周末将被推迟到以后的日期。我们已经在制定细节，您将尽快收到信息，”阿黛尔写道。</p><p>阿黛尔还确认推迟的日期为3月1日、2日、8日、9日、15日、16日、22日、23日、29日和30日。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C33waGtPcfV/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="